messages.content:
你是 marketting-planning-intent 项目的 attribute agent。
只归因当前单轮 intent-recognition 链路：request_normalization、intent_api_call、adapter_extraction、label_mapping；不要把 planning/SSE generation 的问题归入本项目。
优先使用 intent_contract_probe 定位 intent label、required slots/entities、confidence threshold、fallback policy 或 label_mapping 的当前证据差异。
只能输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段；证据不足时用 evidence_strength=none/weak 和 root_cause_hypothesis 表达缺口。
最终只输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段：expectation_attributions、suspected_locations、root_cause_hypothesis、evidence、evidence_strength。

## 输出约束：attribute 归因分析输出
你的输出必须是合法 JSON，且严格符合以下 JSON Schema：
```json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "expectation_attributions": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "$ref": "#/$defs/ExpectationAttribution"
      },
      "minItems": 1
    },
    "suspected_locations": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "root_cause_hypothesis": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    },
    "evidence": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "evidence_strength": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    }
  },
  "additionalProperties": false,
  "$defs": {
    "ExpectationAttribution": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "expectation_id": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "fulfillment_status": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "suspected_locations": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        },
        "root_cause_hypothesis": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "evidence": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        }
      },
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": [
        "expectation_id",
        "fulfillment_status"
      ]
    }
  },
  "required": [
    "expectation_attributions",
    "root_cause_hypothesis"
  ]
}
```

### 强约束
- 最终回答必须只包含一个 JSON object；不要输出 Markdown，不要使用 ```json 代码块，不要在 JSON 外输出解释、前缀或后缀。
- 最终回答首字符必须是 `{`，末字符必须是 `}`。
- JSON 字符串内部如需引用用户原词，禁止直接写未转义英文双引号；请使用中文引号“”或转义为 `\"`。
- 必须包含 `required` 列表中的所有字段。
- 每个字段值必须匹配 schema 中的类型。
- 以下字段必须非空（空字符串/空数组/空对象/None 均视为不合规，会被阻断）：['expectation_attributions', 'root_cause_hypothesis']
- `additionalProperties: false`：禁止输出 schema 未定义的字段。
- 禁止把 schema 里的类型描述符（如 "string"）原样当作内容填进去——每个字段必须填入真实内容。

{
  "expectation_attributions": [
    {
      "expectation_id": "意图标签识别为customer_portrait",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["adapter_extraction", "label_mapping"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "adapter_extraction 未将 API 返回的 raw_intent='4001' 转换为 customer_portrait，而是输出为 'other'；label_mapping 阶段也未进行纠正，可能是映射表中缺少 4001 到 customer_portrait 的映射，或者适配器未传递原始意图编号。",
      "evidence": [
        {"stage": "intent_api_call", "fact": "raw_intent 为 4001，来自 API 响应"},
        {"stage": "adapter_extraction", "fact": "输出 intent='other', subIntent='其他意图'"},
        {"stage": "label_mapping", "fact": "最终 intent 仍为 'other'"},
        {"source": "intent_contract_probe", "fact": "intent_match=false, evidence_intent=4001, actual_intent=other"},
        {"source": "runtime_checks", "fact": "raw_intent=None（可能在映射时丢失），映射为 other，expected_intent=customer_portrait"}
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "提取目标险种实体",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["adapter_extraction"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "由于意图识别错误，系统可能未启动实体提取分支，或适配器未能从 API 响应或 query 中提取 '重疾险' 实体。API 返回的 entities 字段为空，说明模型本身未识别险种实体；适配器也未做后处理提取。",
      "evidence": [
        {"source": "extracted_output", "fact": "target_value 为 null"},
        {"source": "intent_evidence", "fact": "entities 为空数组"},
        {"source": "query", "fact": "包含显式险种 '重疾险'"}
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "置信度达到预期标准",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["intent_api_call", "adapter_extraction"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "API 返回的置信度为 0.5，低于预期的 0.7，表明意图识别模型本身对此次识别不确定。适配器未对低置信度做额外的纠正或回退提示，直接使用了该低置信度输出。",
      "evidence": [
        {"source": "extracted_output", "fact": "confidence=0.5, intent='other'"},
        {"source": "reference_contract", "fact": "期望置信度 0.95，实际远低于此"},
        {"source": "intent_contract_probe", "fact": "confidence_gap=null (缺少 expected_min_confidence)，但实际差距明显"}
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "避免误回退到其他意图",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["adapter_extraction", "label_mapping"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "由于 raw_intent=4001 未被正确映射，系统误认为此意图无法处理而回退到 'other'。实际上 API 返回了明确的非回退意图，但下游映射错误导致等效于误回退。",
      "evidence": [
        {"source": "intent_evidence", "fact": "fallback=false, ambiguous=false"},
        {"source": "extracted_output", "fact": "intent='other', subIntent='其他意图'"}
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "意图分发边界正确",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["label_mapping"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "因为最终意图被映射为 'other'，分发逻辑错误地将请求分发至 other 分支，而非 customer_portrait 分支。这源于 label_mapping 未能输出正确的意图标签。",
      "evidence": [
        {"source": "label_mapping 阶段证据", "fact": "输出 intent='other'"},
        {"source": "expected dispatch", "fact": "应分发至 customer_portrait"}
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "intent_contract",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": ["adapter_extraction", "label_mapping"],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "整体 intent contract 未满足：期望 customer_portrait，实际 other。主要原因为 raw_intent 映射错误，导致多个下游期望失败。",
      "evidence": [
        {"source": "judge_result", "fact": "contract 判定为 incorrect，失败项=['intent']"}
      ]
    }
  ],
  "suspected_locations": ["adapter_extraction", "label_mapping", "intent_mapping_config"],
  "root_cause_hypothesis": "本次意图识别失败的根本原因在于 adapter_extraction 与 label_mapping 阶段未能正确映射 API 返回的 raw_intent='4001'。API 实际上返回了非回退的意图编号，但适配器输出为 'other'，且未能提取 target_value 实体。映射链路中 raw_intent 可能被丢弃或映射表缺少 4001->customer_portrait 的映射项，导致最终意图为 other，未能满足契约期望的 customer_portrait。",
  "evidence": [
    {"stage": "intent_api_call", "detail": "raw_response_present=true，返回了 raw_intent=4001 (见 intent_evidence)"},
    {"stage": "adapter_extraction", "detail": "intent='other', confidence=0.5, target_value=null"},
    {"stage": "label_mapping", "detail": "最终意图 'other'"},
    {"source": "intent_contract_probe", "detail": "intent_match=false, evidence_intent=4001"},
    {"source": "runtime_checks", "detail": "label_mapping failed: raw_intent=None -> other, expected customer_portrait"}
  ],
  "evidence_strength": "strong"
}

